dc_title_s: 1882 Real Estate and Insurance Map of the City of Trenton including Chambersburg, Millham and parts of Ewing, Lawrence and Hamilton Townships: C.C.Haven Trenton Map
dc_description_s: A 1882 real estate and insurance color map of the city of Trenton, NJ, including Chambersburg, Millham and parts of Ewing, Lawrence and Hamilton Townships. The map shows ward boundaries and delineates parcels and building footprints with owners' and businesses' names. Included is a color-coded legend depicting building construction. Fire hydrants and horse and steam railroads are also featured.
